metadata.name: "OUT HERE." a sonic odyssey - (trailer)
metadata.description: “OUT HERE” is a self-reflective audio-visual agglomeration through Latashá’s mythology, taking her audience through her existential breakthrough and dreamscapes meeting reality. With use of electronic, hip hop, jazz, soul, poetic and world sound, Latashá brings us on a sonic journey through her many-selves to find her oneness. A conversation in womanhood, Blackness, spirituality, creativity and evolution, "OUT HERE" is Latashá's guide book into self exploration, love and trust.
